    <p class="fio-p">
      By the end of this lesson, you’ll understand <strong>when, why, and how</strong> to roll covered calls so you can
      manage assignment risk, collect additional premium, and keep your plan structured.
    </p>

    <ol class="fio-list">
      <li>Watch the lesson video (above).</li>
      <li>Read the “When to Roll” decision rules below.</li>
      <li>Use the “Roll Order Checklist” so you don’t miss steps.</li>
